title: Starry Night Bakery and Coffeehouse
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Artsy atmosphere coffeehouse offering fair trade organic coffee, plus smoothies, tea, with soy milk available. Light food menu includes build-your-own and veggie or hummus plates, breakfast egg sandwiches, and some vegan baked goods (labeled). Will make vegan cakes by advance ordering. Has Wi-Fi. Operating since 2002.
